[[File:Marek Jerzy Minakowski przy pracy.jpg|thumb|Marek Jerzy Minakowski in work]] '''Marek Jerzy Minakowski''' (born [[13 June]], [[1972]] in [[Olsztyn]]) – [[Poles|Polish]] philosopher, historian, [[Genealogy|genealogist]], [[Doctor (title)|doctor]] of [[humanities]] and publisher as well as blogger<ref name="minakowski.pl">{{cite web|last1=Minakowski|first1=Marek Jerzy|title=Minakowski.pl|url=http://minakowski.pl/|website=minakowski.pl|accessdate=25 April 2017}}</ref>{{Self-published source|date=March 2018|expert=y|ABOUTSELF=y}} and [[YouTube]]r.<ref name="youtubeMJM">{{cite web|last1=Minakowski|first1=Marek Jerzy|title=Marek Minakowski|url=https://www.youtube.com/user/minakowski|website=YouTube|accessdate=25 April 2017}}{{Self-published source|date=March 2018|expert=y|ABOUTSELF=y}}</ref> Creator of the [[Wielka Genealogia Minakowskiego]] (eng. The Great Genealogy of Minakowski).<ref name="wielcy.plMAIN">{{cite web|last1=Minakowski|first1=Marek Jerzy|title=Wielka Genealogia Minakowskiego|url=http://wielcy.pl/|website=wielcy.pl|publisher=Dr Minakowski Publikacje Elektroniczne|accessdate=25 April 2017}}</ref>{{Self-published source|date=March 2018|expert=y|ABOUTSELF=y}} Co-founder and first marszałek (chairman) of Stowarzyszenie Potomków Sejmu Wielkiego (eng. Society of the Descendants of the [[Great Sejm]]).<ref name="sejmwielkiMJM" />{{Self-published source|date=March 2018|expert=y|ABOUTSELF=y}}
== Life == Marek also graduated from the [[Jagiellonian University]] with the dissertation ''Formal Logic before Aristotle''<ref name="formallogicPhD">{{cite web|last1=Minakowski|first1=Marek Jerzy|title=Prehistoria logiki formalnej (Logika formalna przed Arystotelesem)|url=http://logika.minakowski.pl/|website=logika.minakowski.pl|accessdate=25 April 2017}}</ref>{{Self-published source|date=March 2018|expert=y|ABOUTSELF=y}} which was the result of collecting all traces of the use of formal logic in Greek writing prior to 350 BC (book contains a large catalog of all passages, with original text, translation and logical formalization). Being 26 years old, he was one of the youngest PhDs in Cracow.
In 2016 he received the [[Decoration of Honor Meritorious for Polish Culture]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mkidn.gov.pl/pages/posts/odznaczenia-dla-wybitnych-literaturoznawcow-historykow-i-animatorow-kultury-6637.php|title=Odznaczenia dla wybitnych literaturoznawców, historyków i animatorów kultury MKiDN - 2016|website=www.mkidn.gov.pl|language=pl|access-date=2018-05-31}}</ref>
