The book is a collection of papers "prepared on different occasions as lectures for non-specialist audiences" (p. x).
The author formulates a premise for the book as: ''I may be wrong and you may be right, and by an effort, we may get nearer to the truth'' (p. [https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=qTBpAwAAQBAJ&oi=fnd&pg=PR12&dq=#v=onepage&q&f=false xii]).
